title: Helping Your Kids Navigate Life's Challenges, Part 3
itunes:author: Josh McDowell
itunes:summary: Working parents often struggle with whether they're spending enough time with the kids, but at the end of the day, time is really what kids want most from their parents, even if they don't know it. Receive the book 10 Commitments for Dads with your gift of any amount!
